Sixth limb
(
Table 8
; 
Figure 3F
). Basale with five plumose ventral setae, one plumose seta laterally and one dorsally. First endopodite segment with one ventral seta. Second segment with one seta ventrally and one dorsally. Third segment with three unequal, terminal claw setae; middle claw longest 14.0%CL.

Caudal furca
(
Table 8
; 
Figure 3G
